The paper proposes a model for localizing referents within an image based on referring expressions. This task falls under the computer vision and natural language processing domains, which are covered by the cs.CV and cs.CL categories. The model also involves attention mechanisms and visual attribute prediction, which are common techniques in machine learning and artificial intelligence, covered by the cs.AI category. The paper also reports performance metrics and compares its results with other models, which are typical of the machine learning and data analysis fields, covered by the cs.LG category. Finally, the paper involves image processing and multimodal interaction, which are relevant to the multimedia and human-computer interaction domains, covered by the cs.MM category.
